{"tid":2022583,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"立法會又報警話泛民整傷保安","createTime":"2020-05-18T11:52:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T12:57:41.000Z","uid":7369,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9e7d3cebfed9c7ed38062677800be16cb671e55c","tid":2022583,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:52:31.000Z","msg":"立法會內會今日開會選主席，財委會主席陳健波獲立法會主席梁君彥欽點主持選舉，李慧琼在民主派無投票下當選內會主席，會議期間多名民主派被保安抬走。梁君彥今日晚上發聲明，稱由於有秘書處職員在執行職責時受傷，秘書處已按機制報警。<br />\n<br />\n梁君彥的聲明指，內會今日進行主席選舉期間出現秩序混亂的情況，更有議員多次衝向正在執勤的秘書處職員，導致有保安人員受傷，他對此感到十分遺憾，「由於有秘書處職員在執行職責時受妨礙而受傷，秘書處已根據行管會早前決定的機制報警處理」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%A7%E6%9C%83%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5-%E6%9C%89%E7%A7%98%E6%9B%B8%E8%99%95%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7-%E5%B7%B2%E6%8C%89%E6%A9%9F%E5%88%B6%E5%A0%B1%E8%AD%A6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25BD%25A5-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25A7%2598%25E6%259B%25B8%25E8%2599%2595%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%2582%25B7-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%258C%2589%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6%2F&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCsbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=d3fd8997\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25BD%25A5-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25A7%2598%25E6%259B%25B8%25E8%2599%2595%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%2582%25B7-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%258C%2589%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6%2F&h=bd1bedee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%A7%E6%9C%83%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5-%E6%9C%89%E7%A7%98%E6%9B%B8%E8%99%95%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7-%E5%B7%B2%E6%8C%89%E6%A9%9F%E5%88%B6%E5%A0%B1%